      <!-- KEYBOARD GRAMMAR -->
      <section class="section" id="keyboard">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-num">03 / KEYBOARD<span class="line"></span></div>
            <div>
              <h2>Keyboard-first, <u>mouse-optional</u>.</h2>
              <p>The whole product is under ten shortcuts. Learn them in an hour, save them in a minute. If you know Linear or Vim, you already know most of this.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="kbd-grid">
            <div class="kbd-scope-head">ANYWHERE</div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">command bar</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">⌘</span><span class="plus">+</span><span class="k">K</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Opens the bar. Tab cycles modes. Esc closes.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">ask assistant</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">⌘</span><span class="plus">+</span><span class="k">/</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Straight into ask mode. Same bar, same keyboard.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">capture current tab</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">⌘</span><span class="plus">+</span><span class="k">⇧</span><span class="plus">+</span><span class="k">S</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Save active page to Vault. AI summary + tags, in place.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">new thought</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">⌘</span><span class="plus">+</span><span class="k">N</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Drop a note into the inbox. No template. Just write.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="kbd-scope-head">GO&nbsp;TO · PRESS G, THEN…</div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">today</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">G</span><span class="plus">→</span><span class="k">T</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Jump to the one list that actually matters.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">vault</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">G</span><span class="plus">→</span><span class="k">V</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">All saves. Filter, search, graph view.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">graph</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">G</span><span class="plus">→</span><span class="k">G</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Full-screen backlink graph. Drag, pin, orbit.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">inbox</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">G</span><span class="plus">→</span><span class="k">I</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Everything unfiled. Triage with J/K/E/Shift-3.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="kbd-scope-head">IN&nbsp;ANY&nbsp;LIST</div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">up / down</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">J</span><span class="plus">·</span><span class="k">K</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Vim-style. Select row. Enter opens peek.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">complete</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">X</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Toggle done on any item. No dialog.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">tag</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">#</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Opens tag picker. Type to filter.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="kbd-cell">
              <div class="kbd-cell-label">priority</div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-keys"><span class="k">1</span><span class="plus">·</span><span class="k">2</span><span class="plus">·</span><span class="k">3</span></div>
              <div class="kbd-cell-desc">Set priority. Rose, amber, or none.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

