                <div class="anti-item"><span class="mark">×</span><span class="txt">You want the AI to write for you. (It won't. It'll answer from what you wrote.)</span></div>
                <div class="anti-item"><span class="mark">×</span><span class="txt">You want a weather widget, a motivational quote, a to-do list with checkboxes that jiggle.</span></div>
                <div class="anti-item"><span class="mark">×</span><span class="txt">You want to organize with nested folders. We have tags and backlinks. Pick those.</span></div>
                <div class="anti-item"><span class="mark">×</span><span class="txt">You want a team workspace. We are a single-player tool. On purpose.</span></div>
